WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.006 --> 00:00:02.882
[Daisy]
<i>Previously on </i>The Testaments...

2
00:00:02.966 --> 00:00:04.426
-Mom!
-[June] <i>It was Gilead.</i>

3
00:00:04.509 --> 00:00:06.177
You're in danger.
I need to get you out of here.

4
00:00:06.302 --> 00:00:07.762
