5
00:00:07.846 --> 00:00:10.140
[Aunt Lydia]
<i>Being a woman on God's green earth</i>

6
00:00:10.223 --> 00:00:12.058
<i>is no easy feat.</i>

7
00:00:12.142 --> 00:00:13.893
<i>Who can bring forth God's children?</i>

8
00:00:13.977 --> 00:00:16.062
<i>Who. but you?</i>

9
00:00:16.146 --> 00:00:17.397
[Mr. William]
Dr. Grove is ready for you.

10
00:00:17.480 --> 00:00:19.315
[Dr. Grove] Becka's gonna be thrilled
you're a Green now.

11
00:00:19.399 --> 00:00:21.985
You know. you really are
getting to be a big girl. Agnes.

12
00:00:22.068 --> 00:00:24.529
I imagine your breasts
must be quite tender.

13
00:00:24.612 --> 00:00:27.157
It's starting to move very. very fast.

14
00:00:27.240 --> 00:00:29.492
-It's a dress. not a husband.
-Not yet.

15
00:00:29.576 --> 00:00:32.537
She could get an offer
from a Commander at the dance.

16
00:00:32.620 --> 00:00:35.707
[Aunt Estee] <i>You will have to make many</i>
<i>difficult decisions when you are wives.</i>

17
00:00:35.790 --> 00:00:39.169
I imagine it's a lot to handle.
Being a new wife.

18
00:00:39.252 --> 00:00:41.087
[Penny]
God only sends us what we can bear.

19
00:00:41.171 --> 00:00:43.631
It will be great.
Pushing strollers together.

20
00:00:43.715 --> 00:00:45.633
I don't want to get married.

21
00:00:45.717 --> 00:00:48.720
-I don't want a husband.
-But what else would you do?

22
00:00:48.803 --> 00:00:50.930
-[bus crashing]
-[girls screaming]

23
00:00:51.014 --> 00:00:53.308
Agnes! Get down!

24
00:00:55.393 --> 00:00:57.103
