They don't want to kill you.
They want to take you back.

26
00:00:59.773 --> 00:01:02.484
When you got out of Gilead.
they would not stop looking for you.

27
00:01:02.567 --> 00:01:03.735
Mayday's got you.

28
00:01:03.818 --> 00:01:05.695
[whispering] What the fuck happened?
Was that Mayday?

29
00:01:05.779 --> 00:01:07.155
[Garth]
<i>It was meant to be a retrieval mission.</i>

30
00:01:07.238 --> 00:01:09.240
<i>The girls weren't supposed to get hurt.</i>

31
00:01:09.324 --> 00:01:11.409
-What is this?
-[Daisy] Map of the school.

32
00:01:11.493 --> 00:01:12.827
I need to speak to June.

33
00:01:12.911 --> 00:01:14.829
You guys are just
some sloppy shitshow.

34
00:01:14.913 --> 00:01:17.916
