<i>for a second.</i>

40
00:01:45.944 --> 00:01:47.278
<i>But just a second.</i>

41
00:01:48.488 --> 00:01:51.407
<i>Since the bus attack.</i>
<i>security was everywhere.</i>

42
00:01:51.491 --> 00:01:54.327
<i>I was sure the Eyes were going</i>
<i>to pull me off the street.</i>

43
00:01:54.410 --> 00:01:58.373
<i>Of course. the gals</i>
<i>had their own fish to fry.</i>

44
00:01:58.456 --> 00:02:01.251
