<i>sucking up to the Aunts.</i>

45
00:02:02.043 --> 00:02:04.087
<i>This time. it was a tea party.</i>

46
00:02:04.671 --> 00:02:07.799
<i>The girls stressed out</i>
<i>about buying flowers and sweets</i>

47
00:02:07.882 --> 00:02:09.676
<i>to please the Aunts.</i>

48
00:02:09.759 --> 00:02:11.136
<i>I get it.</i>

49
00:02:11.219 --> 00:02:13.513
<i>Always be extra nice to the frigid sadists</i>

50
00:02:13.596 --> 00:02:15.974
<i>who are arranging your marriage.</i>

51
00:02:16.057 --> 00:02:18.268
